WEBVTT

00:11.830 --> 00:12.830
You...

00:14.720 --> 00:17.070
will all be buried with me.

00:39.390 --> 00:41.120
This is the antidote for Ricin.

00:41.560 --> 00:42.820
I'll give you a choice.

01:00.880 --> 01:02.430
An assassin just broke in

01:02.430 --> 01:03.750
and triggered the Bird Alarm Bell.

01:03.750 --> 01:05.150
The assassin is now dead.

01:05.640 --> 01:06.300
Stand down!

01:11.789 --> 01:12.350
Wait!

01:12.510 --> 01:13.750
Leave the assassin's body here

01:13.750 --> 01:15.950
for His Majesty to verify his identity!

01:37.070 --> 01:37.710
Xing?

01:46.070 --> 01:46.680
Xing,

01:47.350 --> 01:47.920
it's me.

01:50.039 --> 01:51.350
Zhuge Yue...

03:20.810 --> 03:26.070
[REBIRTH]

03:26.530 --> 03:29.100
[Episode 26]

03:33.000 --> 03:33.930
Pass on my order!

03:34.000 --> 03:35.710
Everyone retreat outside the inner palace.

03:35.710 --> 03:37.510
Any trespassers will be killed!

03:46.150 --> 03:47.520
All guards!

03:47.840 --> 03:49.190
His Majesty is unwell.

03:49.520 --> 03:51.670
All guards are ordered to retreat
out of the inner palace courtyard!

03:51.670 --> 03:52.630
No trespassing!

03:52.650 --> 03:53.340
Yes!

04:06.010 --> 04:07.610
Hurry up and check how she is.

04:11.190 --> 04:12.190
No vital organs were hit.

04:12.190 --> 04:13.450
She is just exhausted.

04:13.800 --> 04:14.560
I will go get some medicine to save her.

04:14.560 --> 04:15.090
Alright.

04:36.360 --> 04:37.560
We can only force-feed her the medicine
for now.

04:37.560 --> 04:38.270
If it works,

04:38.290 --> 04:40.220
she will wake up in a couple of days.

04:40.270 --> 04:41.390
You go rest first.

04:41.800 --> 04:43.260
The poison in your body...

04:43.390 --> 04:44.120
I am fine.

05:22.520 --> 05:23.080
Xing!

05:26.320 --> 05:28.360
Just lie down and don't move around.

05:28.500 --> 05:30.720
Don't die
before General Chu actually dies.

05:30.720 --> 05:33.850
I wouldn't know how to explain it to her
when she wakes up.

05:36.550 --> 05:37.240
What is this?

05:37.240 --> 05:38.450
If I'm not mistaken,

05:38.680 --> 05:40.870
this is the antidote to Blood on Snow.

05:43.830 --> 05:45.120
When I was looking for medicine
for General Chu,

05:45.120 --> 05:46.380
I found it by accident.

05:48.720 --> 05:49.520
This smell...

05:50.390 --> 05:51.270
It's wolf vine?

05:51.600 --> 05:53.680
Exactly. It's wolf vine from Ximeng.

05:53.680 --> 05:54.600
It is highly toxic,

05:54.600 --> 05:56.750
but it counteracts Blood on Snow.

05:56.770 --> 05:58.430
So it can be used
to fight poison with poison,

05:58.430 --> 05:59.750
and force Blood on Snow

05:59.750 --> 06:01.410
out of your heart completely.

06:02.410 --> 06:03.310
It's just that...

06:03.310 --> 06:05.190
It's just that wolf vine is highly toxic.

06:05.190 --> 06:07.520
It could be an antidote
or a deadly poison.

06:07.750 --> 06:08.680
Not only that,

06:09.240 --> 06:10.870
besides wolf vine,

06:10.870 --> 06:12.600
there are other herbs in it
whose origin I don't know.

06:12.600 --> 06:14.070
But given the toxicity of wolf vine,

06:14.070 --> 06:16.000
you'll likely fall into a coma
for 7 days after taking it,

06:16.000 --> 06:17.360
with a continuous fever
during the whole time.

06:17.360 --> 06:19.160
If the fever subsides on its own,

06:19.240 --> 06:20.900
you will wake up within 7 days.

06:21.120 --> 06:21.870
If it doesn't...

06:21.870 --> 06:23.240
If it doesn't, you can have my corpse

06:23.240 --> 06:24.300
for your research.

06:27.240 --> 06:27.630
I...

06:28.120 --> 06:28.580
Well...

06:29.070 --> 06:29.870
Really?

06:33.230 --> 06:34.159
What about Xing?

06:34.600 --> 06:35.430
How is she?

06:36.270 --> 06:37.240
She's fine.

06:37.260 --> 06:38.360
I checked her injuries.

06:38.360 --> 06:38.980
There's nothing serious.

06:38.980 --> 06:39.960
She is just exhausted.

06:39.960 --> 06:41.870
She will wake up in a couple of days
after taking medicine.

06:41.870 --> 06:42.630
I've already asked Meng En

06:42.630 --> 06:43.630
to bring Minglu and Wang Shi'er

06:43.630 --> 06:44.430
over here.

06:44.450 --> 06:46.250
Minglu is looking after her now.

06:47.870 --> 06:48.830
I'll go see her.

06:51.430 --> 06:52.180
What about the medicine?

06:52.180 --> 06:53.980
I'll take it after Xing wakes up.

07:13.120 --> 07:13.750
Xing,

07:14.800 --> 07:16.530
since you left Qingshan Manor,

07:17.480 --> 07:19.480
we have had many misunderstandings

07:19.560 --> 07:22.020
and almost been separated
by life and death.

07:24.360 --> 07:26.360
I can't remember how long it has been

07:27.430 --> 07:29.360
since I looked at you this closely.

07:33.870 --> 07:36.530
I always thought
there was no danger in the world

07:36.830 --> 07:38.800
that could not be resolved.

07:40.120 --> 07:41.780
Now, being with you like this,

07:43.390 --> 07:44.480
I am afraid.

07:47.040 --> 07:49.440
I'm afraid I can't make it
until you wake up.

07:55.100 --> 07:56.560
I'm afraid that this time,

07:58.200 --> 08:00.320
death will truly separate us.

08:11.920 --> 08:12.480
My Lord.

08:13.390 --> 08:14.000
My Lord?

08:17.680 --> 08:19.480
Miss Chu's breathing has been steady
these past few days.

08:19.480 --> 08:20.680
She is out of danger.

08:20.870 --> 08:23.270
My Lord, please drink this medicine first.

08:25.950 --> 08:26.870
This smell...

08:27.420 --> 08:28.740
It smells bad,

08:28.770 --> 08:30.300
but it's my newly developed decoction.

08:30.300 --> 08:33.559
It can temporarily suppress
the Blood on Snow in your body.

08:44.150 --> 08:45.030
Rest assured, Young Master.

08:45.030 --> 08:46.830
Miss Chu will certainly be fine.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.360
Why did she pass out so quickly?

08:52.360 --> 08:53.890
Did I use too much medicine?

09:13.070 --> 09:14.190
You sneaky rat!

09:14.210 --> 09:16.440
You don't even make a sound when you walk?

09:16.440 --> 09:17.640
It's just a habit
I've developed from work.

09:17.640 --> 09:19.440
Loud noises might wake the dead.

09:19.580 --> 09:20.180
Well...

09:20.950 --> 09:22.980
Lord Zhuge has had a fever for 3 days.

09:23.390 --> 09:25.320
Aren't you afraid he won't wake up?

09:25.840 --> 09:28.120
He will surely die without the medicine.

09:28.200 --> 09:29.840
Taking it gives him a ray of hope.

09:29.840 --> 09:31.750
I am a miracle doctor
with noble medical ethics,

09:31.750 --> 09:33.000
almost like the reincarnation
of the divine physician Hua Tuo.

09:33.000 --> 09:34.530
How could I leave him to die?

09:35.320 --> 09:36.750
Right.

09:37.000 --> 09:39.790
You are the reincarnation
of legendary doctors.

09:40.240 --> 09:41.600
But just in case—

09:41.720 --> 09:43.440
if he doesn't wake up,

09:43.820 --> 09:45.750
how will you explain it to Lady Chu?

09:46.270 --> 09:48.600
Then I can only hope

09:49.270 --> 09:51.120
that either they both wake up,

09:51.870 --> 09:52.600
or...

09:53.320 --> 09:54.720
neither of them wakes up.

09:54.870 --> 09:56.530
What are you muttering about?

09:58.200 --> 10:00.660
Reaching the same end
by different means...

10:00.720 --> 10:01.960
isn't a bad thing!

10:01.960 --> 10:02.960
Bad news!

10:03.360 --> 10:04.150
Something...

10:04.150 --> 10:05.870
Something terrible happened to Miss Chu!

10:05.870 --> 10:06.720
Miss Chu?

10:06.870 --> 10:08.480
Miss Chu... Miss Chu...

10:08.480 --> 10:09.000
Tell us!

10:09.000 --> 10:09.750
She woke up!

10:09.750 --> 10:10.700
She woke up?

10:11.750 --> 10:13.150
How did it happen so fast?

10:14.480 --> 10:15.390
You didn't tell her

10:15.390 --> 10:17.320
about Young Master Zhuge, did you?

10:28.360 --> 10:29.360
Lady Chu...

10:30.480 --> 10:31.120
Xiao Ran.

10:31.870 --> 10:33.080
Hurry up and check his pulse.

10:33.080 --> 10:34.740
His pulse doesn't seem right.

10:34.960 --> 10:35.510
Minglu,

10:35.840 --> 10:37.640
fetch me a basin of colder water.

10:39.200 --> 10:40.600
What are you waiting for?

10:44.250 --> 10:47.870
♪ The dust in the world ♪

10:48.160 --> 10:51.630
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

10:52.570 --> 10:55.360
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

10:56.040 --> 10:57.390
♪ And not be scared? ♪

10:57.570 --> 10:59.590
♪ A slight ripple ♪

10:59.770 --> 11:03.360
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

11:03.640 --> 11:07.010
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

11:07.760 --> 11:10.600
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

11:11.490 --> 11:14.860
♪ Let it be ♪

11:15.940 --> 11:19.370
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

11:19.740 --> 11:22.750
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

11:23.060 --> 11:24.690
♪ Go weaving ♪

11:25.200 --> 11:30.150
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

11:30.670 --> 11:33.460
♪ We once beheld ♪

11:33.490 --> 11:36.890
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

11:38.530 --> 11:41.140
♪ Beauty never ♪

11:41.170 --> 11:45.900
♪ Lasts for long ♪

11:46.200 --> 11:49.720
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

11:49.750 --> 11:54.180
♪ It's just a stone ♪

11:54.560 --> 12:01.770
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

12:00.550 --> 12:01.200
How is he?

12:01.840 --> 12:02.870
It's been 7 days.

12:04.240 --> 12:06.080
His pulse is chaotic, and the high fever
still hasn't gone down.

12:06.080 --> 12:07.870
It should be caused
by the heat poison of Blood on Snow.

12:07.870 --> 12:08.790
The heat poison is fierce.

12:08.790 --> 12:09.510
If it can't be released,

12:09.510 --> 12:11.120
it will coagulate inside his body.

12:11.120 --> 12:13.390
Then it will be even harder for him
to wake up.

12:13.390 --> 12:14.440
Is there any way?

12:15.750 --> 12:17.480
The fastest way to cool him down

12:19.320 --> 12:21.550
is to soak his whole body in ice water.

12:45.480 --> 12:46.120
Miss Chu,

12:46.840 --> 12:48.040
everything is ready.

12:48.580 --> 12:49.640
Tell them to leave.

12:50.550 --> 12:51.100
Yes.

13:39.270 --> 13:41.180
♪ On the water ♪

13:41.200 --> 13:42.910
♪ Countless ♪

13:42.940 --> 13:44.620
♪ Ripples rise ♪

13:47.150 --> 13:49.220
♪ Through the mortal world ♪

13:49.250 --> 13:52.680
♪ With meetings and goodbyes ♪

13:54.640 --> 13:56.970
♪ How unfair fate is ♪

13:56.990 --> 14:01.990
♪ It gave all the memories back to you ♪

14:02.320 --> 14:03.850
♪ Yet left me ♪

14:03.880 --> 14:07.460
♪ Stuck right here ♪

14:06.550 --> 14:08.000
Xing,

14:08.270 --> 14:09.150
you are...

14:09.590 --> 14:10.810
♪ Rain falls down ♪

14:10.120 --> 14:13.630
an invincible... general.

14:11.160 --> 14:12.560
♪ Lingering thoughts ♪

14:13.330 --> 14:15.560
♪ Awake once more ♪

14:14.600 --> 14:17.080
You can definitely...

14:17.050 --> 14:19.230
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

14:19.470 --> 14:23.120
♪ Another me ♪

14:19.600 --> 14:21.670
take me away.

14:24.320 --> 14:25.510
I know you are still alive,

14:25.050 --> 14:27.050
♪ How can I escape ♪

14:27.000 --> 14:28.960
and I know it was you
who sent the Huotu water.

14:27.080 --> 14:31.840
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

14:30.150 --> 14:31.030
Zhuge Yue,

14:32.240 --> 14:33.550
you've been alive all along.

14:32.460 --> 14:35.440
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

14:34.480 --> 14:36.280
Why have you been hiding from me?

14:36.350 --> 14:39.060
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

14:36.600 --> 14:38.600
Since you chose this path yourself,

14:39.090 --> 14:43.510
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

14:39.200 --> 14:40.480
even if it leads through
a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood,

14:40.480 --> 14:41.790
you will walk it alone.

14:43.480 --> 14:44.440
But if one day,

14:43.700 --> 14:47.300
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

14:44.630 --> 14:47.160
you find you can no longer
take a step forward,

14:47.240 --> 14:48.360
you know the way...

14:47.740 --> 14:49.740
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

14:49.770 --> 14:51.480
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

14:49.840 --> 14:51.170
back to Qingshan Manor.

14:51.510 --> 14:54.110
♪ Searching for your name ♪

14:54.190 --> 14:58.910
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

14:57.240 --> 14:58.940
You've always been protecting me.

14:58.940 --> 15:02.820
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

14:59.840 --> 15:00.510
Now,

15:01.720 --> 15:03.000
it's my turn to protect you.

15:02.840 --> 15:04.840
♪ Melt the ice ♪

15:04.870 --> 15:06.870
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

15:05.440 --> 15:06.200
Zhuge Yue,

15:06.550 --> 15:07.480
you told me

15:06.890 --> 15:12.100
♪ Let the night ♪

15:07.870 --> 15:09.330
that if one day I regret it,

15:09.480 --> 15:10.670
you would be right behind me,

15:10.670 --> 15:12.000
waiting for me to return.

15:12.000 --> 15:12.800
You can't die.

15:13.450 --> 15:18.770
♪ Forever glow ♪

15:13.550 --> 15:14.880
You must always be here.

15:15.030 --> 15:15.840
I promise you.

15:16.510 --> 15:18.710
I want you to stay by my side forever too.

15:19.120 --> 15:20.450
To the ends of the earth,

15:21.120 --> 15:22.520
we live and die together.

15:32.780 --> 15:37.200
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

15:37.400 --> 15:40.990
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

15:41.440 --> 15:43.440
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

15:43.460 --> 15:45.180
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

15:45.200 --> 15:47.800
♪ Searching for your name ♪

15:47.880 --> 15:52.610
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

15:51.480 --> 15:52.960
They're the Sun-Moon Twin Swords.

15:52.630 --> 15:56.520
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

15:53.870 --> 15:54.750
They represent

15:55.600 --> 15:57.240
that we will be together forever.

15:56.540 --> 15:58.540
♪ Melt the ice ♪

15:58.560 --> 16:00.560
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

16:00.590 --> 16:05.800
♪ Let the night ♪

16:07.140 --> 16:12.460
♪ Forever glow ♪

16:19.550 --> 16:23.770
[Capital of Great Yan]

17:05.550 --> 17:06.349
Keep going.

17:07.160 --> 17:08.310
We are almost home.

17:10.109 --> 17:11.589
Keep going. Be good.

17:14.589 --> 17:15.200
Let's go.

17:47.080 --> 17:48.710
Helian, are you alright?

17:52.470 --> 17:53.930
Take me to see His Majesty.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.480
General Cheng, thank you

17:58.480 --> 18:00.270
for sending people to search for me

18:00.270 --> 18:02.310
during the turbulent times in Great Yan.

18:02.310 --> 18:03.510
This is His Majesty's order.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.840
I was just following it.

18:11.320 --> 18:13.580
Thanks for your trouble, General Cheng.

18:27.920 --> 18:28.720
Your Majesty!

18:29.030 --> 18:29.790
What is it?

18:30.160 --> 18:31.160
Your Majesty,

18:31.350 --> 18:33.010
Consort Helian has returned.

18:37.270 --> 18:38.000
I see.

18:38.960 --> 18:40.490
I'm glad she's back safely.

18:41.030 --> 18:42.560
Tell her to go back and rest.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.640
You may leave too.

18:43.680 --> 18:44.200
Yes.

18:46.550 --> 18:47.350
Your Majesty!

18:48.310 --> 18:49.170
Your Highness!

18:51.440 --> 18:52.240
Your Majesty!

18:52.480 --> 18:53.810
No need to pay respects.

18:54.200 --> 18:55.720
I'm glad you're back safely.

18:55.720 --> 18:57.640
I rushed back to the Capital of Great Yan
day and night

18:57.640 --> 18:59.970
because I have something to report to you.

19:11.380 --> 19:12.450
Sister Huan!

19:12.510 --> 19:14.720
Sister Huan, there's a letter for you!

19:14.890 --> 19:16.160
Sister Huan!

19:16.160 --> 19:17.560
There's a letter for you!

19:21.200 --> 19:22.550
Sister Huan. Sister Huan.

19:22.550 --> 19:23.240
There's a letter for you.

19:23.240 --> 19:23.960
There's a letter for you.

19:23.960 --> 19:24.720
Thank you.

19:28.340 --> 19:29.070
Buy yourself some fruits.

19:29.070 --> 19:33.830
I want it too! I want it too!

19:35.200 --> 19:36.400
Go on. Buy yourselves some fruits.

19:36.400 --> 19:38.240
Let's go buy some fruits.

19:38.400 --> 19:40.480
Okay, let's go!

19:40.510 --> 19:41.070
Let's go!

19:42.400 --> 19:43.070
Take care.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.680
As a token of gratitude

19:57.160 --> 19:58.920
for the donkey.

20:01.680 --> 20:04.390
[I will repay your kindness
for lending me the donkey.]

20:06.450 --> 20:07.820
It's you?

21:00.480 --> 21:01.200
Jing,

21:01.680 --> 21:02.880
take the troops away.

21:03.930 --> 21:05.400
Don't disturb the villagers.

21:05.400 --> 21:05.920
Yes!

22:08.590 --> 22:10.450
Your Majesty, please rest early.

22:12.050 --> 22:14.420
We will camp here tonight.

22:15.750 --> 22:16.400
Yes.

23:08.440 --> 23:09.500
Do you remember it?

23:09.920 --> 23:11.180
This is Mountain Snow.

23:15.550 --> 23:16.160
This...

23:17.110 --> 23:18.110
is Mountain Snow?

23:18.350 --> 23:20.480
This was my father's favorite horse.

23:21.510 --> 23:23.240
Once, I secretly rode it out.

23:24.680 --> 23:25.640
It got spooked,

23:26.270 --> 23:27.880
broke off its reins, and ran away.

23:27.880 --> 23:29.310
Afraid of my father's punishment,

23:29.310 --> 23:31.000
I didn't dare to return to the palace.

23:31.000 --> 23:31.920
It was you

23:32.270 --> 23:34.870
who looked for it with me
all night in Mount Hei.

23:34.960 --> 23:38.110
We found it by the Li River in the end.

23:38.270 --> 23:40.200
What exactly are you trying to say?

23:41.200 --> 23:42.110
You once told me

23:42.830 --> 23:44.960
that making mistakes doesn't matter.

23:45.270 --> 23:47.130
As long as you make amends in time,

23:47.310 --> 23:48.440
it's never too late.

23:51.790 --> 23:52.480
Huan Huan,

23:54.400 --> 23:55.640
I lost Great Yan.

23:57.000 --> 23:58.460
Can you help me get it back?

24:03.240 --> 24:06.160
You must have already known the reason

24:06.640 --> 24:10.960
I invited you elders here today.

24:13.880 --> 24:17.720
You'll be deciding

24:18.270 --> 24:20.720
where the future of Great Yan lies.

24:21.510 --> 24:23.110
We will follow the old rules.

24:23.270 --> 24:25.400
Each of you has an eagle feather arrow.

24:25.640 --> 24:27.550
Putting it in the upper censer
means you agree

24:27.550 --> 24:30.640
that the 13 tribes
will secede from Great Yan,

24:30.640 --> 24:33.240
govern themselves, and form an alliance.

24:33.680 --> 24:34.550
Otherwise,

24:36.640 --> 24:38.110
it means you veto it.

24:43.240 --> 24:45.070
Except for the Yan family,

24:46.400 --> 24:49.440
the elders of the 12 tribes are all here.

24:50.070 --> 24:50.960
Please,

24:51.920 --> 24:53.720
after careful consideration,

24:55.240 --> 24:56.350
cast your vote.

25:00.350 --> 25:02.480
This horse is not Mountain Snow at all.

25:02.550 --> 25:04.410
Four years ago, I rode it on a hunt.

25:04.750 --> 25:05.790
To protect me,

25:07.030 --> 25:09.090
it was killed by ferocious wildcats.

25:10.160 --> 25:11.620
What are you trying to say?

25:12.830 --> 25:15.030
Even the horses in Great Yan
know how to repay a favor.

25:15.030 --> 25:16.360
I won't give you a chance

25:16.640 --> 25:18.070
to kill me again.

25:23.880 --> 25:26.750
Elders, what are your decisions?

25:27.590 --> 25:30.310
Great Yan is already beset
by internal and external troubles.

25:30.310 --> 25:32.400
The new King of Great Yan
is not up to the task.

25:32.400 --> 25:34.440
If you cannot see the stakes here,

25:34.910 --> 25:37.000
you can only wait for your doom.

25:38.270 --> 25:41.800
Is the Snowy Region Tribe still
going to sit back and do nothing?

25:44.310 --> 25:45.200
Boy,

25:45.680 --> 25:47.410
do you remember how your sister

25:47.510 --> 25:49.200
was killed?

26:02.790 --> 26:05.880
Our Snowy Region Tribe
made an alliance with the Yan family

26:05.880 --> 26:07.540
to protect Great Yan forever,

26:07.720 --> 26:09.030
and protect the King of Great Yan.

26:09.030 --> 26:11.030
I cannot break my father's promise.

26:12.640 --> 26:14.960
What your father
promised the old King of Great Yan

26:14.960 --> 26:16.270
was to protect Great Yan,

26:16.270 --> 26:17.790
not Yan Xun's family!

26:18.130 --> 26:19.470
Only by making the right choice

26:19.470 --> 26:20.790
for your tribe

26:20.990 --> 26:22.120
are you truly

26:22.310 --> 26:24.110
keeping your father's promise!

26:33.920 --> 26:34.510
An Luo.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.000
General Huan?

26:43.070 --> 26:44.020
General Huan is not dead?

26:44.020 --> 26:44.820
Sister?

26:50.720 --> 26:51.520
General Huan?

26:52.590 --> 26:53.240
Sister!

26:54.920 --> 26:55.850
I thought you...

26:56.400 --> 26:57.330
I thought you...

27:03.750 --> 27:04.390
Your Majesty?

27:04.390 --> 27:05.190
Your Majesty!

27:14.650 --> 27:15.890
Your Majesty.

27:16.270 --> 27:17.070
Your Majesty.

27:23.130 --> 27:24.040
Well done.

27:24.070 --> 27:26.470
You are the pride
of our Snowy Region Tribe.

27:40.790 --> 27:41.590
General Huan.

27:43.030 --> 27:45.480
You have been away from Great Yan
for a long time.

27:45.480 --> 27:46.550
You have no idea

27:46.550 --> 27:47.930
what Great Yan has gone through

27:47.930 --> 27:49.000
during this time.

27:49.020 --> 27:50.420
I'm afraid you can't vote

27:50.720 --> 27:52.880
on behalf of the Snowy Region Tribe now.

27:52.880 --> 27:53.590
Besides,

27:54.000 --> 27:55.830
don't you think you should tell us

27:55.830 --> 27:57.310
where you have been these days

27:57.310 --> 27:59.720
and what happened?

27:59.880 --> 28:00.830
Elder Huo Sang.

28:01.440 --> 28:03.310
Back then,
Great Yan had just opened up trade.

28:03.310 --> 28:06.440
A Great Yong supply caravan
was plundered in the Baichuan Tribe.

28:06.440 --> 28:07.640
The Emperor of Great Yong was furious

28:07.640 --> 28:08.790
and sent troops to demand an explanation.

28:08.790 --> 28:10.830
If it wasn't the old King of Great Yan
who mediated the matter...

28:10.830 --> 28:12.640
As someone who experienced it back then,

28:12.640 --> 28:15.510
Elder Huo Sang,
you must still remember it vividly.

28:16.830 --> 28:18.000
Elder Pale.

28:18.960 --> 28:21.160
Do you know how,
during those extremely cold years,

28:21.160 --> 28:22.790
when you were forced to migrate south

28:22.790 --> 28:24.310
with no food or clothing,

28:24.400 --> 28:25.550
you eventually found

28:25.550 --> 28:26.960
this fertile land?

28:28.240 --> 28:28.840
Oh, right.

28:30.270 --> 28:31.440
Elder Tubu.

28:31.920 --> 28:33.070
Do you still remember

28:33.070 --> 28:34.920
who overcame all objections

28:35.480 --> 28:37.830
to dig a canal
from the other side of Mount Huihui

28:37.830 --> 28:39.440
to bring fresh water
to the Hongchuan Tribe?

28:39.440 --> 28:40.900
Everything you mentioned

28:41.030 --> 28:43.030
was done by the old King of Great Yan.

28:43.480 --> 28:45.590
The old King of Great Yan
was indeed kind to us,

28:45.590 --> 28:47.680
but we have also served him loyally
all our lives.

28:47.680 --> 28:50.310
Now Great Yan is torn apart

28:50.750 --> 28:52.810
and can't withstand any more storms.

28:52.830 --> 28:53.510
Are you

28:54.000 --> 28:56.200
asking us, for this so-called loyalty,

28:56.680 --> 28:59.080
to completely ignore
the fate of Great Yan?

29:08.440 --> 29:10.920
Now, surrounded by tigers and wolves,

29:11.240 --> 29:13.110
the winter of Great Yan is approaching.

29:13.110 --> 29:16.000
If the 13 tribes fall apart,

29:16.110 --> 29:18.310
Great Yan will no longer exist!

29:32.750 --> 29:33.920
This arrow

29:34.750 --> 29:37.480
was made by my father
with his own hands back then.

29:38.350 --> 29:40.720
I've been keeping it with me
all these years

29:40.720 --> 29:42.380
and never let it leave my side.

29:43.110 --> 29:44.680
My previous actions

29:45.590 --> 29:46.790
have failed Great Yan

29:48.110 --> 29:49.400
and failed my father.

29:50.920 --> 29:51.720
But I believe,

29:53.160 --> 29:54.480
if he were here today,

29:56.160 --> 29:58.620
he wouldn't want to see Great Yan
fall apart.

30:02.680 --> 30:04.010
So I'm casting this vote

30:05.720 --> 30:07.400
for my father.

31:14.400 --> 31:15.110
Huan Huan,

31:16.000 --> 31:17.750
the winter of Great Yan is approaching.

31:17.750 --> 31:20.160
The 13 tribes will survive
if we stay together.

31:20.160 --> 31:21.550
If we fall apart,

31:21.680 --> 31:24.440
Great Yan will no longer exist.

31:28.480 --> 31:29.550
I once thought

31:30.480 --> 31:33.440
the Snowy Region Tribe and Great Yan
would share the same fate.

31:33.440 --> 31:35.640
I am your subject and relative,

31:36.200 --> 31:37.730
and I should be loyal to you.

31:38.440 --> 31:40.070
But after facing death once,

31:40.920 --> 31:41.920
I understand now.

31:44.590 --> 31:46.790
I won't be blindly loyal to you anymore.

31:50.480 --> 31:51.940
I will return to Great Yan.

31:52.480 --> 31:53.640
That is my home.

31:54.510 --> 31:55.240
However,

31:56.350 --> 31:58.550
I want 5,000 Black Eagle Army soldiers.

31:58.790 --> 32:01.120
They must be under my command completely.

32:24.070 --> 32:25.160
In today's Ximeng,

32:25.830 --> 32:27.030
all people are equal!

32:27.110 --> 32:28.170
Long live the King!

32:28.510 --> 32:29.790
Long live the Queen!

32:29.880 --> 32:32.130
I am no longer a noble young master
of the Zhuge family.

32:32.130 --> 32:35.440
I can only cling to you and marry into
the Chu family as your matrilocal husband.

32:35.440 --> 32:36.920
By order of His Majesty!

32:37.080 --> 32:38.550
The Seventh Prince
mobilized troops without permission.

32:38.550 --> 32:40.110
He is suspected
of colluding with the enemy to rebel.

32:40.110 --> 32:41.590
The Painting of the Subjugated Queen!

32:41.590 --> 32:42.680
Today,

32:42.880 --> 32:44.720
I will trample on

32:44.720 --> 32:46.510
Yan Xun's dignity.
